[I] Video player built with Qt/QML and libmpv

[T] haruna is a media player built with Qt/QML and libmpv.with features like:
[T] play online videos, through youtube-dl, supports youtube playlists, toggle
[T] playlist with mouse-over, playlist overlays the video, auto skip chapter
[T] containing certain words, configurable shortcuts and mouse buttons, quick
[T] jump to next chapter by middle click on progress bar.

[U] https://apps.kde.org/de/haruna/

[A] The KDE-Team
